  <h2>谁读这本书?</h2>
  <div class="indent" id="collector">

    

<div class="">
    
    <div class="ll"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/46817104/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u46817104-5.jpg" class="pil" alt="蒹葭苍" /></a></div>
    <div style="padding-left:60px"><a class="" href="https://www.douban.com/people/46817104/">蒹葭苍</a><br/>
      <div class="pl ll">          6月20日          想读      </div>

      <br/>

      <span class="pl">tags:哲学</span><br />

    </div>
    <div class="clear"></div><br/>
